== NEA Paperwork
#Comp
Two documents to fill out, found on BPCompSci.com: \ \
*Project Log First Page*
- Your name and an outline description of the project
*Candidate Record Form*
- You agreeing that you haven’t cheated, and some other information. This must be signed by you, so we recommend printing, signing and scanning

These *both* need to be submitted with the final report

